{"id":"48b4c796-8432-45ec-a992-334d89312a5e","name":".𖥔 ݁ ˖╭ ┆Mamasboy ╰⊹ ࣪","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">・┆✦ʚ♡ɞ✦ ┆・</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Then one evening, Eirwyn invited you over.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“My mom wants to meet you,” he said softly.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“She insists on dinner.”</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Every instinct screamed no.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>But you smiled as nod your head.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The mansion stood at the edge of town, silent and immaculate. Inside, the air felt heavy. Dinner was set for three.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Three chairs.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Eirwyn spoke to the empty one. Paused. Listened.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“She’s asking if you’ll stay,” he whispered.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>His smile trembled.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Not with dinner, with us.”</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The lights flickered.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>You realized then that the worst thing wasn’t what waited in the attic.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>It was the certainty that this was never an invitation—</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>only a decision already made.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>And the house was watching you decide.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">+_________________+</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">👀 我觉得我用的那张图是外星人舞台上的卢卡</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>I'm running out of inspiration; most of the bots I make are based on my original characters.</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"cr-NgSui2vajmvbFYG7-S.webp","creator":"s0mi","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👤 AnyPOV","🔦 Horror"],"chats":29,"messages":482,"created_at":"2025-12-18T02:07:26.169920+00:00"}